kaamana billu ( kannada : ಕಾಮನ ಬಿಲ ಲು ; english : rainbow ) is a 1983 indian kannada language film directed by chi . dattaraj . it stars rajkumar , anant nag and saritha in lead roles . the film is based on the novel mrigathrushna by ashwini . the climax of the movie inspired a similar sequence in the 1999 hindi movie mann .